  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/6262b53198baddd75f1e57c1378a1f87.poster.avif?t=1589471680\" width=514 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/6262b53198baddd75f1e57c1378a1f87.webm?t=1589471680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/6262b53198baddd75f1e57c1378a1f87.mp4?t=1589471680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome Brave Explorer</strong></h2><br>You have recently discovered a map to the fabled <strong>Shrine to Anubis</strong> deep in the Kaylo desert. After days of travel you finally find the temple to Anubis's shrine. But who said exploring was going to be easy?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/56fbaabf4e01996deaf3d752930209e2.poster.avif?t=1589471680\" width=478 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/56fbaabf4e01996deaf3d752930209e2.webm?t=1589471680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/56fbaabf4e01996deaf3d752930209e2.mp4?t=1589471680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jump, dodge, and loot your way through increasingly hard levels as you try to find Anubis' final resting place. Just so you can prove to all your other college professors that the ancient Egyptian gods were real!<br><br>Good luck brave adventurer!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1160670/extras/7b21f18b2ef00ed17927d92184de2889.avif?t=1589471680\" width=174 height=179 /></span>",
